snippet.title: Definition of a Circle - Radius of a Circle - MathHelp.com
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on circles, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students learn the definitions of a circle, a radius, a chord, a diameter, a secant, a tangent, congruent circles, concentric circles, an inscribed circle, and a circumscribed circle. Students are then asked to identify or draw these figures in given problems.
